task.summary: Revamped knockout and front end. Added components.
Fixed UPSTART silent failure bugs. -> Replae relative paths with __dirname
Added winston for logging docker commands.
Improved REST API , start GET/POST/PUT calls
Removed Makefiles from Dockie. Functional start, pause, stop, and destroy.
Fixed Pause Unpause, added toggle to UI.
Added Domain functionality. Dockie destroy was updated to completely remove all traces of the container. docker kill && docker rm && docker rmi docker
Removed extra UI and cleaned up.
Created a config file to store database and host information.
Updated configurations and removed some variables.
